Median lobes of the aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Cicindelidae" genus="Cephalota" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cephalota" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="65">Cephalota</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species: 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="65">a</emphasis>
<taxonomicName genus="C." lsidName="C. littorea" pageId="22" pageNumber="65" rank="species" species="littorea">
